    description: "Summer in Montreal is made for exotic cars. Discover our full fleet of luxury rentals perfect for warm-weather drives, festivals, and weekend getaways — starting at $400/day.",
    content: "**Montreal Summer + Exotic Car = Pure Magic**\n\nSummer in Montreal is one of the best times to be alive in this city. The terrasses are packed, the festivals are roaring, the streets are alive — and the open road is calling. There's no better way to experience it all than from behind the wheel of a supercar or luxury vehicle.\n\nAt Exotic Rentals Montreal, our summer fleet is fully available for day rentals, weekend trips, and everything in between.\n\n**Top Summer Rental Picks**\n\n**McLaren 600LT – $1,199/day**\nWith butterfly doors and a 3.8L twin-turbo producing 592 hp, the McLaren 600LT is the ultimate summer showpiece. Open those dramatic doors at a Vieux-Montréal restaurant and watch the crowd react.\n\n**Audi RS5 – $400/day**\nThe most accessible entry into our exotic lineup. A 444 hp turbocharged V6 in a razor-sharp coupe body — perfect for spirited summer driving without breaking the bank.\n\n**R8 V10 – $899/day**\nA naturally aspirated V10 screaming behind your head as you cruise Autoroute 40 on a warm Saturday morning? That's the R8 summer experience.\n\n**Lamborghini Urus – $849/day**\nFor those who want the Lamborghini badge with room for friends and luggage — the Urus was built for summer adventures.\n\n**Summer Activities That Pair Perfectly with an Exotic Rental**\n\n- **Jazz Festival or Osheaga arrivals** — arrive before anyone else notices the music\n- **Laurentians day trip** — wind through mountain roads in a supercar\n- **Old Port evenings** — park, stroll, return to stares of admiration\n- **Quebec City weekend** — 3 hours of highway bliss in an RS6 or M5\n- **Rooftop bar crawl** — because summers should be theatrical\n\n**Why Summer Bookings Sell Out**\n\nSummer is our busiest season. Weddings, corporate events, birthday celebrations, and spontaneous road trips mean our fleet gets reserved weeks in advance. If you have a summer date in mind, contact us as early as possible.\n\n**Beat the summer rush — reserve your exotic rental