    slug: "exotic-car-rental-montreal-film-production",
    title: "Exotic Car Rentals in Montreal for Film & TV Production",
    date: "2026-05-20",
    description: "Need an exotic car for a film shoot, music video, or TV production in Montreal? We offer flexible rental terms, full insurance options, and a camera-ready fleet — contact us today.",
    content: "**Montreal's Go-To Exotic Fleet for Film and TV**\n\nMontreal has emerged as one of North America's premier film production hubs. With generous tax credits, diverse locations, and world-class crews, productions of every scale call this city home. When a scene calls for a high-performance exotic, Exotic Rentals Montreal is the local source.\n\nOur vehicles have appeared in commercial shoots, music videos, and branded content — and we know exactly what production teams need.\n\n**Why Productions Choose Us**\n\n**Camera-ready vehicles:** Our fleet is maintained in show-room condition. Clean engine bays, spotless interiors, and pristine bodywork — ready for close-ups.\n\n**Flexible scheduling:** Productions don't run on 9-to-5 schedules. We accommodate early call times, multi-day holds, and last-minute changes.\n\n**Variety:** Need to shoot multiple scenes with different vehicles? Our fleet gives you options:\n\n- **McLaren 600LT** – $1,199/day — low, aggressive, dramatic angles\n- **Lamborghini Urus** – $849/day — the luxury SUV that looks at home anywhere\n- **G63 AMG** – $999/day — imposing presence, urban authority\n- **Audi RS6** – $649/day — understated performance for realism-driven content\n- **BMW M5** – $499/day — executive menace, perfect for thriller aesthetics\n\n**Common Production Uses**\n\n- **Hero car** scenes requiring high-performance vehicles\n- **Establishing shots** and drive-bys with real exhaust sounds\n- **Music videos** requiring aspirational imagery\n- **Commercial spots** for automotive, luxury, or lifestyle brands\n- **Background vehicles** for high-end location shoots\n\n**What We Need From You**\n\nFor production rentals, we ask for:\n\n- Production company details\n- Shoot dates and location(s)\n- How the vehicle will be used (driving, static, hero, background)\n- Insurance or production coverage confirmation\n\nWe work with productions directly or through location scouts and production coordinators.\n\n**Competitive Rates for Multi-Day Holds**\n\nFor multi-day rentals or production holds, we offer custom pricing. The longer the booking, the better the rate. Reach out with your dates and we'll build a quote that works for your budget.\n\n**Get a Production Quote Today**\n\nDon't leave your hero car scene to chance. Book a camera-ready exotic that shows up perfectly every time.\n\n📲 **WhatsApp us with your production details:** [+1 (514) 773-8079](https://wa.me/15147738079)\n\nOr email your brief to: contact@exoticrentalsmontreal.com\n\nLights, camera, horsepower.",
