    slug: "exotic-car-rental-montreal-long-weekend",
    title: "Make Your Long Weekend Epic – Exotic Car Rental in Montreal",
    date: "2026-05-20",
    description: "Long weekends in Montreal deserve extraordinary experiences. Rent an exotic car for 2-3 days and turn your holiday into something you'll talk about for years.",
    content: "**Long Weekend? Don't Waste It in an Ordinary Car**\n\nLong weekends are rare. They show up a handful of times a year and disappear just as fast. Why spend one running errands in a family sedan when you could be hammering a V10 up the Laurentians in an Audi R8?\n\nAt Exotic Rentals Montreal, multi-day rentals are one of our most popular options — and for good reason. A 2 or 3-day exotic rental gives you time to actually experience the car instead of just showing it off for an evening.\n\n**Long Weekend Itinerary Ideas**\n\n**The Mountain Loop (2 days)**\nDay 1: Montreal → Mont-Tremblant. Drive the scenic route through Saint-Sauveur. Evening at the pedestrian village.\nDay 2: Mountain roads in the morning. Return to Montreal via Route 117.\nBest vehicle: **BMW M5 ($499/day)** or **Audi RS6 ($649/day)**\n\n**The Maritime Run (3 days)**\nDay 1: Montreal → Quebec City (RS6 on the 20, windows down)\nDay 2: Quebec City exploration\nDay 3: Return via the south shore\nBest vehicle: **Audi RS7 ($499/day)** — luxury meets highway performance\n\n**The Local Luxury Weekend**\nNo road trip required — just live your best Montreal life.\nFriday evening arrival at your hotel in a G63. Saturday brunch in the Plateau. Sunday Old Port. Return Sunday evening.\nBest vehicle: **G63 AMG ($999/day)** or **Lamborghini Urus ($849/day)**\n\n**Multi-Day Rental Benefits**\n\n- **Better value per day** — longer rentals often include favorable pricing\n- **More flexibility** — no rush to return the car\n- **More memorable** — a full weekend in a supercar vs. a few evening hours is incomparable\n- **Road trip ready** — actually get somewhere worth going\n\n**Upcoming Long Weekends in Quebec**\n\nPlan ahead for Victoria Day, Fête Nationale, Labour Day, and Thanksgiving. These weekends fill our calendar quickly. Early booking is strongly recommended.\n\n**Reserve Your Long Weekend Exotic Today**\n\nDon't let another holiday pass in an ordinary car. Book your long weekend exotic rental before your dates are gone.\n\n📲 **WhatsApp us to lock in your long weekend:** [+1 (514) 773-8079](https://wa.me/15147738079)\n\nOr email: contact@exoticrentalsmontreal.com\n\nYou've earned the long weekend. Make it count.",
