  {
    slug: "montreal-supercar-rental-payment-options",
    title: "Supercar Rental in Montreal – Payment Options & Booking Guide",
    date: "2026-05-20",
    description: "Wondering how to pay for a supercar rental in Montreal? Learn about our accepted payment methods, deposit requirements, and how to book your exotic vehicle easily.",
    content: "**Booking a Supercar in Montreal Shouldn't Be Complicated**\n\nOne of the most common questions we get is: how does the payment process actually work for an exotic car rental? Fair question — renting a $200,000 supercar is different from booking a regular rental. Here's exactly how it works at Exotic Rentals Montreal.\n\n**Our Accepted Payment Methods**\n\nWe accept the following payment options:\n\n- **Credit card** — Visa, Mastercard, and American Express accepted\n- **Debit card** — subject to pre-authorization hold\n- **Bank transfer** — for larger or multi-day bookings, a wire transfer can be arranged\n- **Cash** — accepted with valid ID and a standard security deposit\n\nWe work to make the financial side as smooth as the driving experience. Contact us directly to discuss your preferred method.\n\n**Security Deposit — What to Expect**\n\nAll rentals require a refundable security deposit, which varies by vehicle. The deposit is held during the rental period and fully released upon the vehicle's return in its original condition.\n\nDeposit amounts reflect the value and tier of the vehicle rented:\n\n- **Entry tier** (RS5, RS7, M5): Standard deposit\n- **Mid tier** (RS6, R8, Urus): Elevated deposit\n- **Top tier** (McLaren 600LT, G63): Premium deposit\n\nWe'll quote your specific deposit amount when you confirm your booking.\n\n**Booking Process Step by Step**\n\n1. **Contact us** — via WhatsApp or email with your desired vehicle, date, and pickup/delivery preference\n2. **Confirm availability** — we check the calendar and hold your date\n3. **Agreement & deposit** — you receive a rental agreement and pay the deposit to secure the reservation\n4. **Vehicle delivery or pickup** — on the day, the car comes to you or you pick it up\n5. **Return and release** — car is inspected on return, deposit released\n\n**Eligibility Requirements**\n\n- Minimum age: 25 years old\n- Valid full driver's license (minimum 2 years)\n- Clean driving record\n- Valid credit/debit card or accepted payment form\n\n**Have Questions About Payment?**\n\nWe're always happy to walk you through the process before you commit to anything. Our team responds quickly on WhatsApp.\n\n📲 **WhatsApp us with your booking questions:** [+1 (514) 773-8079](https://wa.me/15147738079)\n\nOr email: contact@exoticrentalsmontreal.com\n\nSimple process. Serious cars.",
