    content: "**Your Exotic Car, Delivered to Your Hotel Door**\n\nYou're staying at a downtown Montreal hotel. You've got a big evening planned — dinner, an event, maybe just a long scenic drive through the city at night. The last thing you want is to arrange transportation to a rental office. That's why we offer direct hotel delivery anywhere in Montreal.\n\n**How Hotel Delivery Works**\n\nIt's exactly as convenient as it sounds:\n\n1. **Book your vehicle** via WhatsApp or email — tell us your hotel and arrival time\n2. **We confirm the delivery window** — typically within a 1-hour slot that works for you\n3. **We bring the car to you** — a team member delivers the vehicle to your hotel's entrance or parking area\n4. **You drive** — your rental begins the moment the keys are in your hand\n5. **Return at your convenience** — we arrange pickup at your hotel or your next destination\n\nNo taxi to a remote lot. No waiting rooms. Just your exotic car, ready at your hotel.\n\n**Hotels We Regularly Deliver To**\n\nWe deliver to properties across Montreal including:\n\n- Downtown core (Sheraton, Marriott, Westin, Four Seasons area)\n- Vieux-Montréal (Hotel Nelligan, Auberge du Vieux-Port)\n- Plateau-Mont-Royal and Mile-End boutique hotels\n- Airport-adjacent hotels for arriving international clients\n\nIf your hotel isn't listed — no problem. If you're in Montreal, we can reach you.\n\n**Perfect For**\n\n- **Business travelers** arriving for client meetings or conferences\n- **Tourists** wanting to explore Montreal and beyond in style\n- **Special occasions** — birthdays, anniversaries, proposals\n- **Event arrivals** — galas, concerts, sports events\n\n**Our Delivery Fleet**\n\nEvery vehicle in our fleet is available for hotel delivery:\n\n- Audi RS5 – $400/day\n- BMW M5, Audi RS7 – $499/day\n- Audi RS6 – $649/day\n- R8 V10 – $899/day\n- Lamborghini Urus – $849/day\n- G63 AMG – $999/day\n- McLaren 600LT – $1,199/day\n\n**Reserve Your Hotel Delivery Today**\n\nTell us your hotel, your date, and your preferred vehicle. We handle the rest.\n\n📲 **WhatsApp us to arrange hotel delivery:** [+1 (514) 773-8079](https://wa.me/15147738079)\n\nOr email: contact@exoticrentalsmontreal.com\n\nMontreal's finest cars. Delivered to your door.",
