  {
    slug: "exotic-car-delivery-westmount-ndg-plateau-montreal",
    title: "Exotic Car Delivery to Westmount, NDG, and Plateau Montreal",
    date: "2026-05-22",
    description: "Get an exotic car delivered directly to Westmount, NDG, or Plateau Montreal — doorstep supercar delivery for the ultimate convenient luxury experience.",
    content: "<h2>Door to Door Exotic Car Delivery in Montreal Neighborhoods</h2><p>One of the most common questions we receive at Exotic Rentals Montreal is simple: do you deliver? The answer is an emphatic yes. We bring our world class fleet of Lamborghinis, Ferraris, McLarens, and other supercars directly to your door, anywhere in Montreal. Whether you live in a stately Westmount home, a chic Plateau Mont Royal loft, a Notre Dame de Grace family estate, or a downtown penthouse, we deliver your dream car to your exact location.</p><p>You should never have to take a taxi or Uber to pick up an exotic car rental. That is why our concierge delivery service is a core part of what we offer. We handle the logistics so you can focus entirely on enjoying the experience.</p><h2>Neighborhoods We Deliver To in Montreal</h2><h3>Westmount</h3><p>Westmount is home to some of Montreal most prestigious addresses, and our vehicles are a familiar sight in its tree lined streets. We regularly deliver Lamborghini Urus SUVs, Mercedes G63 AMGs, and Porsche 911 TechArt editions to Westmount clients for everything from weekend drives to corporate events and special celebrations. If you are hosting guests or attending a gala event, we will have your vehicle waiting freshly detailed and ready to go.</p><h3>Notre Dame de Grace</h3><p>NDG is a neighborhood that blends residential charm with urban sophistication. Our clients in NDG frequently rent BMW M5 Competitions and Audi RS7s for weekend getaways to the Eastern Townships or the Laurentians. We deliver directly to your home address and pick up when your rental period ends, making the entire experience completely seamless.</p><h3>Plateau Mont Royal</h3><p>The Plateau is Montreal cultural heartland and home to artists, creatives, entrepreneurs, and professionals who appreciate the finer things. Our deliveries to the Plateau often involve vehicles rented for birthday celebrations, photoshoots, anniversary surprises, and content creation. The charming streets and architecture of the Plateau also make a spectacular backdrop for exotic car photography.</p><h3>Other Neighborhoods We Serve</h3><p>Beyond Westmount, NDG, and the Plateau, we deliver throughout all of Montreal including Outremont, Mile End, Rosemont, Griffintown, Old Montreal, Verdun, Côte des Neiges, and the city center. We also extend our delivery service to Laval, Longueuil, Brossard, and all South Shore communities.</p><h2>How the Delivery Process Works</h2><p>Booking a delivered exotic car rental in Montreal is simple. Contact our team at (438) 533 9053 with your preferred vehicle, date, and delivery address. We will confirm availability, arrange a delivery window that works for your schedule, and handle everything from there.</p><p>On the day of your rental, one of our team members drives your chosen vehicle to your address. We conduct a brief walkthrough of the vehicle together, go over the controls and features, answer any questions you have, and then the car is yours for the agreed rental period. At the end of your rental, we arrange pickup from whatever location is most convenient for you.</p><h2>Our Fleet Available for Delivery</h2><p>Every vehicle in our fleet is available for delivery across Montreal. This includes our full Lamborghini lineup featuring the Urus SUV, Huracán Tecnica, EVO, and EVO Spyder. Our Italian and British supercars including the Ferrari 488 GTB, McLaren 570GT, and McLaren 600LT are equally available for delivery. Our luxury performance fleet of Audi RS5, RS6, RS7, and R8, BMW M3, M5, X5M, and X6M, and Mercedes G63, E63S, and S63 can all be delivered to your door.</p><p>Prices start at $350 per day for our performance vehicles and reach up to ];,400 per day for our flagship supercars. Delivery fees vary by location and will be confirmed when you book.</p><h2>Why Montreal Clients Love Our Delivery Service</h2><p>Our clients consistently tell us that the delivery experience sets Exotic Rentals Montreal apart from every other rental company they have tried. Picking up an exotic car from a nondescript rental lot is a very different experience from having a gleaming Lamborghini or Ferrari delivered to your front door. The concierge delivery model matches the premium nature of the vehicles we provide.</p><p>If you are planning a special occasion, a weekend adventure, or simply want to experience the joy of driving one of the world finest automobiles, call us today at (438) 533 9053. We deliver directly to Westmount, NDG, Plateau Mont Royal, and every corner of Montreal and its surrounding areas. Your supercar experience starts the moment we pull up to your door.</p>",
  },
