    description: "The McLaren 570GT is the grand tourer that never lets you forget it's a supercar. Rent it in Montreal and take it east on the 10 — the Eastern Townships were made for this car.",
    content: "<h2>McLaren 570GT — A Weekend Drive Through the Eastern Townships</h2><p>The Eastern Townships are one of Quebec's best-kept road secrets. Route 243 through Sutton, the rolling hills between Knowlton and Bromont, the long straights that open up past Granby heading toward Sherbrooke — these roads were designed for a car like the McLaren 570GT. Not a track weapon. Not a daily driver. The GT: McLaren's most liveable supercar, built for exactly this kind of weekend.</p><p>Where the 600LT is focused and demanding, the 570GT is balanced. The same 562hp twin-turbo V8, but with a softer suspension calibration, a longer wheelbase, and a small cargo shelf behind the seats that can actually carry luggage for a weekend trip. It's still a mid-engine supercar with a soundtrack that fills any tunnel with sound. But it adds a layer of usability that makes the two-hour drive from Montreal to the Townships feel intentional rather than heroic.</p><p>Rent the 570GT on a Friday afternoon and have it delivered to your building. Take the 10 east, let the car settle in, and discover what a McLaren feels like when you stop trying to go fast and just drive. Saturday morning in Bromont, the car in the background of the lake, early light — you won't need a filter.</p><p>Ready to book? Text or call us at <strong>(438) 533 9053</strong> or message us on <a href=\"https://wa.me/14385339053\">WhatsApp</a>. We deliver to your hotel, home, or any Montreal landmark. Fully detailed, full tank, ready to go.</p>",
