    content: "<h2>Audi RS6 Avant — The Greatest Sleeper You Can Rent in Montreal</h2><p>The Audi RS6 Avant exists to make a very specific point: performance doesn't have to announce itself. From the outside, it looks like a very clean wagon — wide body kit, RS badges on the grille, matte black 22-inch wheels if you're paying attention. From the inside, it seats five adults in genuine comfort with 565 litres of cargo space behind the rear seats. And under the hood, a 591hp twin-turbo V8 that launches this car to 100 km/h in 3.6 seconds. Most people never see it coming.</p><p>The RS6 is the car you rent when you want to be remarkable without being obvious. In a parking lot full of Uruses and G-Wagens, the RS6 Avant sits quietly and waits. On the highway toward Quebec City, it dispatches everything else while the family in the back seat remains completely comfortable. This duality is what Audi's RS division does better than anyone — build something technically extraordinary inside a body that could pass for a high-end executive vehicle.</p><p>At 549 dollars per day, it's also one of the best value propositions in the fleet. You get more power than the BMW M4, more practicality than almost anything else on the list, and the kind of everyday usability that makes a long weekend rental genuinely fun from the first kilometre to the last.</p><p>Ready to book? Text or call us at <strong>(438) 533 9053</strong> or message us on <a href=\"https://wa.me/14385339053\">WhatsApp</a>. We deliver to your hotel, home, or any Montreal landmark. Fully detailed, full tank, ready to go.</p>",
